extendedInfo.description: Honeywell Users Group for Buildings Symposium is a 4-day educational event where customers have the opportunity to network with industry peers, explore different problem-solving approaches and discover best practices implemented by other attendees. The 2013 symposium will be held at the Fairmont Scottsdale Princess, June 9-13. Further details at www.honeywellinteract.com Note: This app is restricted to conference attendees only through password protectionKeywords: Honeywell, Users Group, HUG, Honeywell Users Group, Honeywell Users Group for Buildings
